How to get ready to use WBRU TuneGenie to Spotify converter:
01) Clone and install requests from: https://github.com/kennethreitz/requests
    (install the package by navigating to the cloned directory and running:
    'python setup.py install' you may have to run this command as su in order
    to have permission to the correct directories, all python packages are 
    installed in this manner)
02) Clone and install spotipy from: https://github.com/plamere/spotipy
03) Ensure that SSL is installed by opening python and running 'import ssl'
    if there is an error with that command then SSL is not installed so
    download and install it from: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ssl/
04) At this point you should be all set to get up and running!

